Facilyn: The gross profit analysis check asks: "Which enterprises contribute most to covering overheads?" This helps you focus on activities that generate the best income relative to their additional costs.

Facilyn: Think about your example decision in terms of income generation versus the extra costs it would create.

How does your decision perform on this check?

