@need_clarification_gpa
title: I need help understanding this analysis
tags: gpa_options

Me: I need help understanding this analysis.

Facilyn: Think of gross profit as income minus the direct additional costs of that specific activity. For example, if you're considering a new service, what extra income would it generate, and what extra costs would it create? The difference is its contribution to covering your fixed overheads.

Facilyn: Compare different activities to see which ones are most financially efficient at supporting your overall operations.

